WEBVTT

00:07:27.958 --> 00:07:30.355
but if we kill off ideas
from the beginning,

00:07:30.379 --> 00:07:34.178
it limits our creativity
and dampens the design process.

00:07:34.861 --> 00:07:37.924
Kids, on the other hand,
think about possibilities.

00:07:39.099 --> 00:07:41.519
For kids, the sky is the limit.

00:07:41.543 --> 00:07:42.693
Literally.

00:07:43.609 --> 00:07:47.807
When we worked with middle-school students
to design teen-friendly parks,

00:07:47.831 --> 00:07:51.387
they drew pictures
of skydiving, hang gliding,

00:07:51.411 --> 00:07:53.220
(Laughter)

00:07:53.244 --> 00:07:56.680
and jumping from trampolines
into giant foam pits.

00:07:56.704 --> 00:07:58.136
(Laughter)

00:07:58.780 --> 00:08:00.875
Some of this sounds far-fetched,